Installation notes
--------------------------

Before starting the application, you must configure the JBoss AS7.

Profile
-------

Profile with the settings located in the directory "assets/jboss", its contents must be copied to the server directory.
To start the server, you must use the script "bin/standalone-openjst.sh"

ModeShape
---------

Additionally you need to download and install ModeShape 3.1.3.Final (http://www.jboss.org/modeshape/downloads).
From the downloaded archive "ModeShape subsystem for AS7.1" (modeshape-3.1.3.Final-jbossas-71-dist.zip) requires only
two directories: docs, modules. These directories must be copied to JBoss, overwriting existing files.
